<div class="single">
<h1 class="single-title mt-4 mb-2">The looming copper crunch and why recycling can’t fix it</h1>
<div class='post-meta mb-4'>
<a href='/external-author?author=Nelson Bennett - Business in Vancouver'>Nelson Bennett - Business in Vancouver</a> | July 25, 2022 | 11:28 am <span class="tags">
<a href="https://www.mining.com/category/intelligence/">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mining.com/region/canada/">Canada</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mining.com/region/europe/">Europe</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mining.com/region/usa/">USA</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://www.mining.com/commodity/copper/">Copper</a>&nbsp; </span>
</div>
<div class="post-inner-content row">
<div class="col-lg-8 order-0">
<div class="featured-pic-container ratio-16-9 mb-3">
<div class="img-content">
<img width="1024" height="576" src="https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-1024x576.jpeg" class="attachment-large size-large wp-post-image" alt="The looming copper crunch and why recycling can’t fix it" srcset="https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-1024x576.jpeg 1024w, https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-300x169.jpeg 300w, https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-1536x864.jpeg 1536w, https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-2048x1152.jpeg 2048w, https://www.mining.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/copper-car-scaled-e1658245109266.jpeg 900w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /> </div>
</div>
<div class="img-caption mb-3">Stock Image </div>
<p>In 2021, global electric vehicle&nbsp;sales hit 6.6 million – more than double the 3 million in sales in 2020 &#8212; meaning EVs made up 9% of the global car market last year.</p><div class='d-flex justify-content-center mb-3'><script type="text/javascript"> var rnd = window.rnd || Math.floor(Math.random() * 10e6); var pid472436 = window.pid472436 || rnd; var plc472436 = window.plc472436 || 0; var abkw = window.abkw || ''; var absrc = 'https://servedbyadbutler.com/adserve/;ID=181210;size=0x0;setID=472436;type=js;sw=' + screen.width + ';sh=' + screen.height + ';spr=' + window.devicePixelRatio + ';kw=' + abkw + ';pid=' + pid472436+ ';place=' + (plc472436++) + ';rnd=' + rnd + ';click=CLICK_MACRO_PLACEHOLDER'; document.write('<scr' + 'ipt src="' + absrc + '" type="text/javascript"></scr' + 'ipt>'); </script></div>
<p>That’s the good news, from a decarbonization standpoint.</p> </div>
<div class="col-lg-4 order-2 order-lg-1 order-xl-1">
